<p>
If you liked this game, try the <a href="http://www.colloquial.com/VoiceXML">Other
VoiceXML applications on Colloquial</a>.

<p>
Here's the <a href="eightcall.vxml">VoiceXML source code for the Magic
Eight Call</a>.  It exercises most of the basics of the language
including JavaScript functions, variables, forms and control flow.
This appliction is compliant with the <a
href="http://xi.nu/8ball/answers.html">official 8-ball answers</a>.


<P>
VoiceXML is a new technology that enables you to write voice
dialogues in much the same way as you write HTML.  
You can find the spec and further information at
<a href="http://www.voicexml.org">The VoiceXML Forum</a>.

